  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 3 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Three members of the gang who stole mobile phones for 3 months were arrested in Jaffna",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police said that three members of the gang who had been stealing mobile phones for 3 months in Jaffna have been arrested.",
        "The police said that 43 mobile phones worth around Rs 15 lakh have been seized from the suspects.",
        "The suspects, aged 23, 24 and 27, from Navakuzhi and Ariyalai were arrested yesterday by the crime prevention unit of the Jaffna headquarters police station.",
        "45 mobile phones, including an iPhone worth around Rs 3 lakh, have been seized from the suspects.",
        "The police said that the suspects had confessed that they boarded the buses and stole mobile phones from the passengers due to drug addiction.",
        "The police said that they are also related to the theft of mobile phones in the Jaffna teaching hospital.",
        "The police also mentioned that if the mobile phone is stolen, the concerned people can come to the Jaffna headquarters police station and identify it."
      ],
